snippet.title: Last Plast - GamePlay
snippet.description:
Download the game here: https://giladschreiber.itch.io/the-last-plast

Based on Xonix game made in 1984 by Ilan Raab and Dani Katz. Help the blue fallow to capture areas while avoiding jellyfish, with some additional powerups and obstacles to upgrade your experience.

Guide: Dani Bacon, Animation: Omri Leshnick, Technique: Claymation, Platform: Unity
